<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٩- حُمَيضَة بْنُ الشَّمَردَل.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنِ الْحَارِثِ بْنِ قَيس، يَرْوِي عنهُ ابْن أَبي لَيلَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هو الأَسَدِيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يُعَدُّ فِي الكُوفيين.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِيهِ نَظَرٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>